This privacy policy pertains to the SpatialFin app.

SpatialFin does not collect or access any personal information. No identifying information or user data of any kind is made available to third-parties.

SpatialFin connects exclusively to Jellyfin servers that are configured by the user. All media data, credentials, and server communication remain solely between the user's device and the user's own Jellyfin server. SpatialFin does not transmit any data to the developer or any external service.

This Privacy Policy is effective as of March 14th, 2025 and will remain in effect except with respect to any changes in its provisions in the future, which will be in effect immediately after being posted on this page. We reserve the right to update or change our Privacy Policy at any time and you should check this Privacy Policy periodically. Your continued use of the Service after we post any modifications to the Privacy Policy on this page will constitute your acknowledgment of the modifications and your consent to abide and be bound by the modified Privacy Policy.

